      "otherNotes": "Xp points: 11 + 40 + 15 + 10 - 65 = 11 remaining.\n\nHybrid form is Large.\n\nWhen using blood rite, if rolling a 19 or 20 on attack, get an extra die of damage.\n\n\nWhile transformed, you can expend the following actions (= proficiency bonus per long rest): 1. give an encouraging howl to allies = pick three allies in range, including self. Those three allies gain pack tactics this turn. \n\n\nMan destroyed the world for coin, power, truth, and magic, all for nothing. (Rose spirits)",
