    {
      "name": "Aria Mao",
      "race": "Kender",
      "classes": [
        {
          "name": "Rogue",
          "level": 6,
          "subclassName": "Assassin",
          "subclassDescription": "<p><em>Practice the Grim Art of Death</em></p>\r\n<p>An Assassin’s training focuses on using stealth, poison, and disguise to eliminate foes with deadly efficiency.</p>"
        }
      ],
      "alignmentId": null,
      "background": "Far Traveler",
      "personalityTraits": "I have my own ideas about what is and is not food, and I find the eating habits of those around me fascinating, confusing, or revolting.\nI have different assumptions from those around me concerning personal space, blithely invading others’ space in innocence, or reacting to ignorant invasion of my own.",
      "ideals": "Reserved. As someone new to these strange lands, I am cautious and respectful in my dealings. (Lawful)\nCunning. Though I may not know their ways, neither do they know mine, which can be to my advantage. (Evil)\nSuspicious. I must be careful, for I have no way of telling friend from foe here. (Any)",
      "bonds": "I’m fascinated by the beauty and wonder of this new land.\nMy freedom is my most precious possession. I’ll never let anyone take it from me again.",
      "flaws": "I pretend not to understand the local language in order to avoid interactions I would rather not have.\nI have a weakness for the new intoxicants and other pleasures of this land.",
